data.description: Welcome to the epitome of comfort and elegance! This remarkable one owner, two-story home, spanning over 2500 square feet, offers a perfect blend of functionality and style. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. The lower level features two hallway closets for added storage convenience, while the focal point of the living area is a captivating wood-burning fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Enhancing the functionality of the kitchen is a brand-new gas stove and a refrigerator, both installed in 2023 and included with the home. Upstairs you'll find a versatile game room that can easily be transformed into a fourth bedroom to suit your evolving needs. The master bedroom is a sanctuary, complete with a spacious walk-in closet, a separate shower, and a garden tub. Outside, a 10 by 12 storage unit provides ample space for all your storage needs.New wood fence installed in 2022. This home has never experienced flooding. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home.
